items.title: The Race to Save a Salamander That Spawned a Global Cottage Industry
items.description: From TikTok to McDonald’s Happy Meals, Mexico’s ancient axolotl is everywhere, except where it is supposed to be—in the wild.

items.title: Safe Compounder McDonald’s Stock (MCD) Demands Reassuring Premium
items.description: McDonald’s (MCD) stock has proven highly resilient in recent weeks against the broader market’s brutal sell-off, once again reminding us of its safe compounder status. While the fast-food goliath is dealing with inflation headwinds and shifts in consumer spending, it recently celebrated all-time record revenues and earnings.
